      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 5,
        "x": 19,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Extended XGBoost\n**Best overall** \u00b7 **Preferred family**\n\n- **Type:** enhanced gradient boosting\n- **Purpose:** Improved prediction using extended telemetry features\n- **Accuracy:** 98.13%\n- **Energy:** 1245 J\n- **Interpretation:** Best overall accuracy and stability across the evaluated telemetry-driven models.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "title": "Extended XGBoost",
      "transparent": false,
      "type": "text"
