      "id": 12,
      "options": {
        "content": "## AI Outcome Panel\n\nAI-based telemetry modelling enabled predictive energy modelling without requiring a physical water-cooling testbed. The results support energy-aware workload orchestration in constrained data-centre environments.\n\n**Interpretation**\n\nThe AI layer does not replace infrastructure telemetry. Instead, it converts telemetry into a predictive control signal that can guide workload placement, reduce unnecessary energy overhead, and support constrained data-centre operations when physical heat-reuse experimentation is not available.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "title": "AI Outcome Panel",
